    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craftaway is a fresh take on roguelike card games. Battle cute but dangerous enemies, collect powerful cards, and upgrade your gear as you explore and face surprises head on, make strange new friends, and put your skills to the test to uncover the secrets of the island!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/ea0304d1e69c783c62624d398e732ebf.poster.avif?t=1770948869\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/ea0304d1e69c783c62624d398e732ebf.webm?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/ea0304d1e69c783c62624d398e732ebf.mp4?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a shipwreck you find yourself on a mysterious island where no one can die. Explore the island to uncover its secrets, endure it's many dangers, and eventually find your way home.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOURSELF</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/6646b3286df3859c66b5e2f4f570e68c.poster.avif?t=1770948869\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/6646b3286df3859c66b5e2f4f570e68c.webm?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/6646b3286df3859c66b5e2f4f570e68c.mp4?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a <strong>class</strong> and <strong>customize</strong> your character at any time! Be as beautiful as you are in real life, or completely whacky. The choice is yours!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BATTLE </strong><span class=\"bb_strike\">CUTE</span> <strong>POWERFUL ENEMIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/b8e6fbec808f165a285f9e61f19e7c8e.poster.avif?t=1770948869\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/b8e6fbec808f165a285f9e61f19e7c8e.webm?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/b8e6fbec808f165a285f9e61f19e7c8e.mp4?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the island battling cute but powerful enemies! Each one requires different strategies--use your cards wisely!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR CARDS &amp; GEAR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/adbc243f796d2498ba80f173aa29018f.poster.avif?t=1770948869\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/adbc243f796d2498ba80f173aa29018f.webm?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/adbc243f796d2498ba80f173aa29018f.mp4?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn new cards and equipment as you progress. Pick the most optimal gear, or just go for what makes you look the coolest!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KARMA &amp; RANDOM ENCOUNTERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/421e25daa84a1ae2fef8db9137471678.poster.avif?t=1770948869\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/421e25daa84a1ae2fef8db9137471678.webm?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/421e25daa84a1ae2fef8db9137471678.mp4?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Across your journey you'll find many interesting characters. Some want to help, but others, well... Just stay sharp, you never know what's around the corner!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, your good or bad actions give <strong>Karma</strong>. For example: Robbing a helpless man in need might end up <i>very</i> bad for you down the line -- but help him instead, and you'll find <i>very</i> nice rewards later.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD A TEAM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/093072024b1133a00d86ac40d159394d.poster.avif?t=1770948869\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/093072024b1133a00d86ac40d159394d.webm?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256410/extras/093072024b1133a00d86ac40d159394d.mp4?t=1770948869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why go alone when you can bring some pals? Recruit helpers, mercenaries, or even monsters to fight with you in combat!</p>",
